{"tid":682081,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美軍兩艘驅逐艦　闖中國西沙領海","createTime":"2018-05-28T14:30:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-29T11:41:18.000Z","uid":25558,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"ba6b8cd7471d7f83266ffabd53aa1600f610c499","tid":682081,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T14:30:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180528/20403381\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180528%2F20403381&d=a%2FgG8cP4M3Rftnet3o2OSv1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=7ee020ac\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180528%2F20403381&h=5b0af249\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180528/20403381</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年05月28日 <br />\n<br />\n美軍兩艘驅逐艦　闖中國西沙領海<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180528/large/28cx22p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180528%2Flarge%2F28cx22p.jpg&h=b1fcc0aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■美軍驅逐艦希金斯號。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n南海風雲再起。美國兩艘軍艦希金斯號導彈驅逐艦（USS Higgins）、安提坦號導彈巡洋艦（USS Antietam），昨日駛入中國西沙群島12海里範圍，並一度在趙述島、東島、中建島、永興島等中方佔有的島礁附近巡航；擺明挑機中方在西沙部署轟6K轟炸機。中國軍方暫未有回應。<br />\n<br />\n路透社引述兩名美國官員證實，美軍上述兩艦昨在南海西沙群島進行「自由航行」任務，駛入西沙群島諸多島礁12海里內，包括中國填海造地、興建機場、部署導彈的永興島，這也是管轄南海的三沙市行政中心。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n針對華部署轟6K<br />\n<br />\n上周二（5月22日）美軍兩架B52轟炸機、加油機曾飛進南海空域「執行訓練任務」。有專家分析指，美軍的行動明顯是針對中國軍方早前宣佈轟6K部署南海島礁而來。中國軍方媒體日前高調宣揚轟6K在西沙永興島起降消息，外界視之為中方進一步對南海軍事化。<br />\n<br />\n近年來美方為抗議中國在南海填海造陸、將島礁軍事化，頻派軍艦戰機到南海，進入中方島礁12海里領海領空，擺明不承認中方填海填出來的「主權範圍」。中國外交部批評美方的舉動是在炫耀武力。<br />\n<br />\n目前中國除在西沙的永興島擁有可起降民航客機和戰機的機場外，在南沙的渚碧礁、美濟礁和永暑礁也用填海方式填出三個機場，令中方等同在南沙擁三艘不沉航母。<br />\n<br />\n路透社  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n全球僱員七萬　家電巨企多是非<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n加皇家銀行官網　將台列中國省分"},{"pid":"81bf1f171643458446355a588342ffbdcb773742","tid":682081,"uid":26156,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T14:36:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"55c31a5366237964e2075973979f3dfa4645b2c4","tid":682081,"uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T14:37:25.000Z","msg":"其實有咩意義"},{"pid":"d4d468754ce9b28b2c42689bb9483c3cf45c3254","tid":682081,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T14:38:48.000Z","msg":"不沉航母。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"952e450763ee4b2f602205547910074279e790cb","tid":682081,"uid":34103,"like":1,"dislike":17,"score":-16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T14:40:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e85329f2bcfe2ba3fa7c76dafc69ec4e1c195c60","tid":682081,"uid":118976,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T14:51:21.000Z","msg":"不沉航母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咪即係唔識郁嘅死靶"},{"pid":"20a97c12e8731a5ec4e97afa72fdf47d4f96a409","tid":682081,"uid":35930,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T14:53:36.000Z","msg":"標題黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n人地係一艘導彈驅逐艦，一艘導彈巡洋艦"},{"pid":"c914d9b16cf49b5c82a9fd29ea92ecf1cb7e8936","tid":682081,"uid":104699,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T15:02:05.000Z","msg":"人地刀光劍影，小支支把劍都未亮到"},{"pid":"41a41b145b754870b33c6925a2a82b8b70b6168d","tid":682081,"uid":79442,"like":