83266ffabd53aa1600f610c499","tid":682081,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T14:30:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180528/20403381\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180528%2F20403381&d=a%2FgG8cP4M3Rftnet3o2OSv1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=7ee020ac\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180528%2F20403381&h=5b0af249\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180528/20403381</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年05月28日 <br />\n<br />\n美軍兩艘驅逐艦　闖中國西沙領海<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180528/large/28cx22p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180528%2Flarge%2F28cx22p.jpg&h=b1fcc0aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■美軍驅逐艦希金斯號。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n南海風雲再起。美國兩艘軍艦希金斯號導彈驅逐艦（USS Higgins）、安提坦號導彈巡洋艦（USS Antietam），昨日駛入中國西沙群島12海里範圍，並一度在趙述島、東島、中建島、永興島等中方佔有的島礁附近巡航；擺明挑機中方在西沙部署轟6K轟炸機。中國軍方暫未有回應。<br />\n<br />\n路透社引述兩名美國官員證實，美軍上述兩艦昨在南海西沙群島進行「自由航行」任務，駛入西沙群島諸多島礁12海里內，包括中國填海造地、興建機場、部署導彈的永興島，這也是管轄南海的三沙市行政中心。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n針對華部署轟6K<br />\n<br />\n上周二（5月22日）美軍兩架B52轟炸機、加油機曾飛進南海空域「執行訓練任務」。有專家分析指，美軍的行動明顯是針對中國軍方早前宣佈轟6K部署南海島礁而來。中國軍方媒體日前高調宣揚轟6K在西沙永興島起降消息，外界視之為中方進一步對南海軍事化。<br />\n<br />\n近年來美方為抗議中國在南海填海造陸、將島礁軍事化，頻派軍艦戰機到南海，進入中方島礁12海里領海領空，擺明不承認中方填海填出來的「主權範圍」。中國外交部批評美方的舉動是在炫耀武力。<br />\n<br />\n目前中國除在西沙的永興島擁有可起降民航客機和戰機的機場外，在南沙的渚碧礁、美濟礁和永暑礁也用填海方式填出三個機場，令中方等同在南沙擁三艘不沉航母。<br />\n<br />\n路透社  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n全球僱員七萬　家電巨企多是非<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n加皇家銀行官網　將台列中國省分"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T15:03:41.000Z","msg":"唔郁得既航母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T15:52:29.000Z","msg":"想當年意大利果條友吹到意大利自己就係不沉航母, 結果後尾俾英國炸到出唔到海<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n歷史果然係不斷重復"},{"pid":"80d44f3c86c2ea1158c7704591dfe5783700be99","tid":682081,"uid":30001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2bd7c367c49766d04c0d96d49c2dc9a8fb79eb79","tid":682081,"uid":18955,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T15:25:52.000Z","msg":"Higgins 岩岩先去Syria 射完戰斧<br />\n又去南海遊船河 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一定累到仆街 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nUS NAVY IS THE BEST <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T15:52:57.000Z","msg":"幾時過黎南海撚下狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f61f965f3db176fee2a5ecebfbc75cd5f9324793","tid":682081,"uid":165360,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T15:54:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b312d59a08d36bb7d75ddb7997c80f1cc2b6f065","tid":682081,"uid":57675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T16:05:11.000Z","msg":"幾時到我帶路<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3d9d2bd50efe4abde7131a0d62c84eb8648a17e","tid":682081,"uid":44105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T16:20:52.000Z","msg":"蟈幾時出兵維護領土完整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e124d0d41ba25b17378af4fbd2d6551bd3bb1cd2","tid":682081,"uid":76710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T16:28:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.congress.gov/bill/115th-congress/house-bill/5680?q=%7B%22search%22%3A%5B%22H.R.5680%22%5D%7D&amp;r=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.congress.gov%2Fbill%2F115th-congress%2Fhouse-b